resources.string:
In order to establish connection with the remote partner,
    follow these steps:
    1. Select \"Start session\" button at the main screen;
    2. Choose session type;
    3. After a little delay you will see a screen with your address. Copy this info and send to your
    partner via other messenger;
    4. Ask your partner to send you their address as well;
    5. Enter partner address in the corresponding field;
    6. Press \"Connect\" button.
    If connection was successfully established, you will see a chat screen. If you want to finish session,
    open three-dots menu and press \"Disconnect\" button. The session will be finished, you will be no
    longer able to send messages. Session messages will be saved, you can access them by pressing the \"Saved sessions\"
    button at the main screen.
